'''Mahmoud Saber Abdelmohsen Hassan Abdelmohsen''' ({{langx|ar|مَحْمُود صَابِر عَبْد الْمُحْسِن حَسَنْ عَبْد الْمُحْسِن}}; born 30 July 2001) is an Egyptian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[central midfielder]] for [[Egyptian Premier League]] club [[ZED FC|ZED]] on loan from [[Pyramids FC|Pyramids]] and the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt national team]].

==Club career==
Saber started playing football in [[Nogoom FC|Nogoom]], where he made his debut in the [[Egyptian Premier League]] on 22 May 2019 in a 2–0 loss to [[Pyramids FC|Pyramids]]. In November 2020, he went on loan to Pyramids, and at the end of the season, he was purchased permanently.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elbalad.news/4976385|title=بيراميدز يضم محمود صابر نهائيا من النجوم|language=ar}}</ref> He scored his first goal on 25 August 2023 against [[Misr Lel Makkasa SC|Misr Lel Makkasa]].

In 2023, Saber was loaned to [[ZED FC|ZED]], but after just six months he returned to Pyramids.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youm7.com/story/2024/1/29/%D9%85%D8%AD%D9%85%D9%88%D8%AF-%D8%B5%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%B1-%D9%8A%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%B8%D9%85-%D9%81%D9%89-%D8%AA%D8%AF%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A8%D9%8A%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%8A%D8%AF%D8%B2-%D8%A8%D8%B9%D8%AF-%D9%82%D8%B7%D8%B9-%D8%A5%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%AA%D9%87-%D9%84%D9%80/6462915|title=محمود صابر ينتظم فى تدريبات بيراميدز بعد قطع إعارته لـ زد.. صور|language=ar}}</ref>

==International career==
Saber was included in the [[Egypt national under-23 football team|Egyptian U-23 squad]] for the [[Football at the 2024 Summer Olympics – Men's tournament|Olympic Games]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/EFA/status/1808927725484233057|title=قائمة منتخب مصر الأوليمبي لمعسكر الإعداد المقرر انطلاقه غدا الجمعة 5 يوليو استعدادا لأولمبياد باريس 2024|trans-title=Mr. Rogério Micale reveals the list of players heading to Paris|language=ar|publisher=[[Egyptian Football Association]]|website=Twitter|date=4 July 2024}}</ref>

On 2 December 2025, Saber was called up to the Egypt squad for the [[2025 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cafonline.com/afcon2025/news/egypt-name-final-28-man-squad-for-totalenergies-caf-afcon-2025-salah-leads-pharaohs-charge/|title=Egypt name final 28-man squad for TotalEnergies CAF AFCON 2025, Salah leads Pharaohs' charge|publisher=[[Confederation of African Football]]|date=2 December 2025|access-date=12 December 2025}}</ref>

